The lowest-frequency rotational absorption is the $J=0 \rightarrow 1$ line. $$h \nu=E_{\mathrm{upper}}-E_{\mathrm{lower}}=\frac{1(2) \hbar^2}{2 \mu d^2}-\frac{0(1) \hbar^2}{2 \mu d^2}
